{"title_page": "CocoSori", "text_new": "{{short description|South Korean musical duo}}\n{{Infobox musical artist\n| name            = CocoSori\n| background      = group_or_band\n| image           = CocoSori in 2016.jpg\n| landscape       = \n| caption         = CocoSori in 2016\n| alias           = \n| origin          = South Korea\n| genre           = {{hlist|[[K-pop]]|[[J-pop]]}}\n| years_active    = {{start date|2016}}\u20132019\n| label           = Mole Entertainment\n| associated_acts = \n| website         = {{url|molent.co.kr}}\n| past_members = \n* Coco\n* [[Sori (singer)|Sori]]\n}}\n'''CocoSori''' ([[Hangul]]: \ucf54\ucf54\uc18c\ub9ac) was a South Korean duo formed by Mole Entertainment.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.search.naver.com/search.naver?where=nexearch&sm=tab_ppn&query=%EC%BD%94%EC%BD%94%EC%86%8C%EB%A6%AC&os=3207131&ie=utf8&key=PeopleService|title=\ucf54\ucf54\uc18c\ub9ac \ud504\ub85c\ud544|publisher=Naver|language=ko}}</ref> They debuted on January 5, 2016, with the single \"Dark Circle\".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tenasia.hankyung.com/archives/1423170|title=\ucf54\ucf54\uc18c\ub9ac, \uc0c8 \ubbf8\ub2c8\uc568\ubc94 '\ubbf8 \uc544\ubaa8\ub974' \ucef4\ubc31\u20261\ub144 8\uac1c\uc6d4\ub9cc\uc758 \ucef4\ubc31|publisher=Ten Asia|language=ko}}</ref> On February 1, 2019, through a direct statement from Mole Entertainment, CocoSori was announced to have disbanded due to internal conflicts with member Coco.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/cocosori22/posts/2102359213190227|title=CocoSori \ucf54\ucf54\uc18c\ub9ac|website=www.facebook.com|language=en|access-date=2019-02-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.allkpop.com/article/2019/02/cocosori-to-officially-disband-mole-entertainment-announces-legal-action-against-coco-lee|title=CocoSori to officially disband, MOLE Entertainment announces legal action against Coco Lee|website=allkpop|access-date=2019-02-04}}</ref> \n\n==Discography==\n===Single albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowhead